div.div: Commented on #840 feat: update table example and table.tape

The examples are really about showing a specific behavior. The table example should be less about showing off tailwind / material / being able to switch schemes. and More about showing off the features of the table. I'd suggest keep it muted, and keep the color changes to the end of the gif, cycliing through with at least 1 sec and perhaps 2 secs. To avoid "jumping" when the user reaches the end of the loop, you'll either need a longer pause at the end or make sure to make it back to where the loops starts.
